subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Women)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: As they prepare for the N.C.A.A. women’s basketball semifinals, Notre Dame Coach Muffet McGraw and UConn’s Geno Auriemma each have a story to tell.
